function Start(idActorPlayer, sLevelAreaName)
	
	for i, Player in ipairs(Hydra.ActorsInTriggerBounds(idWakeUpTrigger)) do
		if bIsSelfInTrigger == false then
			bIsSelfInTrigger = Hydra.ActorIsPlayer(Player)
		end
	end
	
	if bIsSelfInTrigger == true then
		Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idSelf, powerWakeUp)
	end
	
	idTaissaClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(idTaissaSleeping)
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idTaissaClone)
	Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idTaissaClone)
	
end
